latestPosts.caption:
Makeup can be so many things. The whole process of figuring out what you enjoy and what you want to do can be so much fun but also very challenging at times. 

Getting into the creative field was a risk I decided to take not knowing the difficulties and hurdles that awaits. The biggest of them all tho? Instability. It’s hard to keep yourself motivated at all times and keep your head above the water. 

Social media has given a lot of people great opportunities but it has also taken away a lot from some people. The constant pressure of always trying to have a perfectly aesthetic feed, number of followers, likes, views, etc. can definitely take a toll on anyone. It did on me, for sure. 

So, I have come back once again, with only one goal this time; to enjoy my art. The freedom it gives me to express and create and not give a fuck about “perfection”, coz it doesn’t exist. 
So I’m gonna begin from the beginning and have the best time. 
COZ THIS BARBIE DESERVES IT! 💅💓
